documentation.overview:
The iOS navigation bar user interface for visual presentation.

Make a proposed icon to be a component then select and swap it in the app bar component if you propose to replace current icon by the proposed icon.

interfaces.content:
Send the message `navbar_collpase_with_value` to the navigation bar component with scrollOffset of the contents that the navigation bar located with, the navigation bar can be collapsed or expanded accroding to the scroll position.

The `Container.scrollOffset` can be obtained via `send response` by Detect Trigger when a scroll container is scrolled.

documentation.overview: The iOS switch can be toggled on and toggled off.

interfaces.content: Send the message `toggle_on` to the switch component when the switch needs to be toggled on.
Send the message `toggle_off` to the switch component when the switch needs to be toggled off.
After the switch has been toggled on, the message `toggled_on` is received from the switch component.
After the switch has been toggled off, the message `toggled_off` is received from the switch component.

documentation.overview:
The iOS slider can adjust a value within a certain range. 

The minimum, maximum, and initial value of the slider can be set. The current value changes when the slider is dragged.

interfaces.name: minValue
interfaces.content: Set the minimum value for the slider.

interfaces.name: maxValue
interfaces.content: Set the maximum value for the slider.

interfaces.name: initialValue
interfaces.content: Set the minimum value for the slider.

interfaces.name: roundUpNumber
interfaces.content:
This indicates whether current value includes a decimal point or not.
When set to  `true` , current value is an integer value that has been rounded up.
When set to  `false` , current value is a value with two decimal places.

Send the message `slider_change_with_value` to the slider component when the thumb image of the slider needs to be moved based on a certain value. 
A value can be sent along with the the message.

Every time the slider is dragged, the message `slider_changed_with_value` is received from the slider component.
The value, received along with the message, can be assigned to a variable.

documentation.overview:
The stepper component with two-segment button to increase or decrease an incremental value. 

The minimum / maximum / initial value of the incremental value can be set in stepper, and the  incremental value can be displayed from stepper. Any interaction can be triggered when the stepper button is tapped.

interfaces.name: minValue
interfaces.content: Set the minimum value for the stepper.

interfaces.name: maxValue
interfaces.content: Set the maximum value for the stepper.

interfaces.name: initialValue
interfaces.content: Set the initial value for the stepper.

interfaces.name: step
interfaces.content: Set the increase / decrease step value for the stepper.
After the - button has been tapped, the message `button_down_tapped` is received from the stepper component.
After the + button has been tapped, the message `button_up_tapped` is received from the stepper component.

After the + / - button on the stepper has been tapped, the message `stepper_changed_with_value` is received from the stepper component, and the incremental value is received along with the message.

The value, received along with the message, can be assigned to a variable.

documentation.overview: The iOS picker can select a value from certain values.

interfaces.content: Send the message `picker_open` to the picker component when the picker needs to be opened.
After the Done button has been tapped, the message `done_tapped_with_value`  is received from the picker component, and the selected value is received along with the message
After the down arrow has been tapped, the message `up_arrow_tapped` is received from the picker component.
After the down arrow has been tapped, the message `down_arrow_tapped` is received from the picker component.

documentation.overview: The iOS search bar can be input with text content.

interfaces.content: Send the message `input_focus_in` to the search bar component when the search bar input box needs to be focused in.
Send the message `input_focus_out` to the search bar component when the search bar input box needs to be focused out.
After text has been typed, the message `input_typed_with_value` is received from the search bar component, and the input text is received along with the message.
After the search bar input box has been focused in, the message `input_focused_in` is received from the search bar component.
After the search bar input box has been focused out, the message `input_focused_out` is received from the search bar component.
After return key has been pressed, the message `return_pressed_with_value` is received from the search bar component, and the input text is received along with the message.

documentation.overview: The action sheet of iOS. Typically the action sheet is hidden in default, and it can be opened when specified button is tapped.

interfaces.content: Send the message `action_sheet_open` to the action sheet component when the action sheet needs to be opened.
After the cancel button has been tapped, the message `cancel_tapped` is received from the action sheet component.
After the button has been tapped, the message `button_tapped` is received from the action sheet component.
